OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and the chance of
OL,6,Fa few showers this morning, these
OL,7,Fmainly at first. This afternoon will
OL,8,Fbe dry with some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fintervals.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen thickening cloud will bring rain
OL,13,Facross all parts for a time overnight.
OL,14,FRain turning light and patchy later on.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FDry and cloudy in the
OL,17,Fmorning. Rain will spread northeast
OL,18,Facross all parts for a time during the
OL,19,Fafternoon, drier by evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
